    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "CQgrA2va4Jzx"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Preprocessing"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "NS5O4-Vtq-N1"
      },
      "source": [
        "SEQ_LEN = 100\n",
        "\n",
        "def to_sequences(data, seq_len):\n",
        "    d = []\n",
        "\n",
        "    for index in range(len(data) - seq_len):\n",
        "        d.append(data[index: index + seq_len])\n",
        "\n",
        "    return np.array(d)\n",
        "\n",
        "def preprocess(data_raw, seq_len, train_split):\n",
        "\n",
        "    data = to_sequences(data_raw, seq_len)\n",
        "\n",
        "    num_train = int(train_split * data.shape[0])\n",
        "\n",
        "    X_train = data[:num_train, :-1, :]\n",
        "    y_train = data[:num_train, -1, :]\n",
        "\n",
        "    X_test = data[num_train:, :-1, :]\n",
        "    y_test = data[num_train:, -1, :]\n",
        "\n",
        "    return X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test = preprocess(scaled_close, SEQ_LEN, train_split = 0.80)"
      ],
      "execution_count": 15,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "XNBTUeaXreni",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "outputId": "4ad101c0-598f-48f7-93de-2100a5fdab03"

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Yhhv26c34YTW"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Model"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "a3dw5qTasJoy"
      },
      "source": [
        "DROPOUT = 0.2\n",
        "WINDOW_SIZE = SEQ_LEN - 1\n",
        "\n",
        "model = keras.Sequential()\n",
        "\n",
        "model.add(Bidirectional(CuDNNLSTM(WINDOW_SIZE, return_sequences=True),\n",
        "                        input_shape=(WINDOW_SIZE, X_train.shape[-1])))\n",
        "model.add(Dropout(rate=DROPOUT))\n",
        "\n",
        "model.add(Bidirectional(CuDNNLSTM((WINDOW_SIZE * 2), return_sequences=True)))\n",
        "model.add(Dropout(rate=DROPOUT))\n",
        "\n",
        "model.add(Bidirectional(CuDNNLSTM(WINDOW_SIZE, return_sequences=False)))\n",
        "\n",
        "model.add(Dense(units=1))\n",
        "\n",
        "model.add(Activation('linear'))"
      ],
      "execution_count": 18,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "pjBan-K27L8d"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Training"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zvc-LMgOHkWJ"
      },
      "source": [
        "model.compile(\n",
        "    loss='mean_squared_error', \n",
        "    optimizer='adam'\n",
        ")"
      ],
      "execution_count": 19,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "m1aU2xDvsvrN",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "outputId": "2563c680-5d75-4685-a559-44c46d4455f3"
      },
      "source": [
        "BATCH_SIZE = 64\n",
        "\n",
        "history = model.fit(\n",
        "    X_train, \n",
        "    y_train, \n",
        "    epochs=50, \n",
        "    batch_size=BATCH_SIZE, \n",
        "    shuffle=False,\n",
        "    validation_split=0.1\n",
        ")"
      ],
